{"tid":2370334,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝笑到個傻鳩同事面都黃埋","createTime":"2021-01-18T03:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T08:24:21.000Z","uid":31447,"like":12,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"214cf21edacc35d7387840e979d3f88ef9b4d79e","tid":2370334,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"今朝返到公司<br />\n成班同事係到討論緊搭車定揸車好<br />\n我咪八卦走埋去一齊聽<br />\n<br />\n女同事:香港交通網絡好方便，洗鬼養車咩，養車仲要咁貴<br />\n<br />\n傻鳩同事(搭狗鐵)：養車其實冇你想像中咁貴，保險牌費燕梳一年都係萬幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n我哋成班同事:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女同事:吓，保險咪姐係燕梳，insurance呀，講兩次做咩啫<br />\n<br />\n傻鳩同事仲死撐:你唔好傻啦，保險即係車保，燕梳係第三者保險呀<br />\n<br />\n最後終於輪到我上場<br />\n我: 傻鳩同事你柒左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班同事笑到佢面都黃<br />\n清潔個阿姐仲笑到牙都甩埋<br />\n<br />\n我仲偷偷地放咗本英漢字典喺個傻鳩同事枱面<br />\n笑能死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b720eb022dd80fc37a5e48c61c75588e66473af","tid":2370334,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3f2a5f0f2075e2b4916a9b5e545909832da0d4","tid":2370334,"uid":31447,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"咩事咁多負評<br />\n負評俾狗屌"},{"pid":"3cf20637c3932722bf29f3451fbd9ef2695bed81","tid":2370334,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"認同請按讚"},{"pid":"189c5f91053cfffa61d30224a602c41c3448c3b4","tid":2370334,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"5/10<br />\n<br />\n😂👌👌"},{"pid":"f5521944a9743a72a3e2422b4653bc7fe1077424","tid":2370334,"uid":257683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:22:40.000Z","msg":"好笑，但又未至於好好笑"},{"pid":"c3a5c4e672a4382de5d0e35c15c068db8438802d","tid":2370334,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"189c5f91053cfffa61d30224a602c41c3448c3b4","tid":2370334,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"5/10<br />\n<br />\n😂👌👌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"真人真事改編"},{"pid":"a33fe53669fff7b80f2c1294b0d9181a10907a90","tid":2370334,"uid":169195,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"一般啦<br />\n唔值開post 打咁多字"},{"pid":"b542475aef1e9c07af64703afc0e538f943dec24","tid":2370334,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"笑。"},{"pid":"812ebc308be90fb7efd016dfda739f821772d697","tid":2370334,"uid":231079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"無是咁的 0分"},{"pid":"6be2744acd5b62a3f33d209023137433da64f1e9","tid":2370334,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy